About Me    Wrapping an Image with the text   body { margin: 20px; text-align: center; } h1 { color: green; } img { float: left; margin: 40px; } p { text-align: justify; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.5; }  
    Greetings. I am Damien Wong/SuperTsumu, a beginner cyber security engineer from Malaysia & CTF player for Team Excelsior. I am currently studying for a diploma in ICT specializing in software engineering at Asia Pacific University of Technology and Innovation.
